05:32.320 --> 05:36.240
Dhoni! Dhoni! Dhoni! Dhoni!

05:36.320 --> 05:40.160
Dhoni! Dhoni! Dhoni! Dhoni!

05:40.240 --> 05:43.200
Dhoni! Dhoni! Dhoni! Dhoni!

06:17.600 --> 06:18.720
Pan Singh Dhoni?

06:21.040 --> 06:22.920
Congratulations, it's a boy.

06:24.040 --> 06:25.080
Mr. Ghosh.

06:25.200 --> 06:26.720
Congratulations, it's a girl.

06:26.800 --> 06:28.120
Thank you.

06:28.920 --> 06:31.520
Rascals, you have a sister.

06:34.280 --> 06:35.480
Both are okay, Dhoni.

06:35.560 --> 06:37.200
Mother and daughter.

06:37.880 --> 06:41.720
But Doctor,
the nurse just said

06:41.920 --> 06:42.960
it's a boy.

06:43.000 --> 06:45.320
Huh! Did she say boy?
- Yes.

06:46.200 --> 06:47.280
Just a minute.

06:51.560 --> 06:54.920
What did Pan Singh Dhoni have?
- A boy.

06:54.960 --> 06:57.440
And Ghosh?
- Girl.

06:58.200 --> 06:59.360
Oh!

07:01.480 --> 07:03.720
You're right. It's a boy.

07:03.880 --> 07:06.960
And Mr. Ghosh, congratulations
for the baby girl.

07:07.480 --> 07:08.560
Okay?

07:12.560 --> 07:13.640
Unbelievable.

07:14.520 --> 07:17.160
If they continue like this someday
the babies will get exchanged!

07:22.640 --> 07:23.840
Mr. Dhoni.

07:39.320 --> 07:41.440
Just don't argue with him.
- Okay, sir.

07:41.520 --> 07:43.040
Just listen to what
he says and say yes.

07:43.080 --> 07:45.640
Right, sir. - Actually,
Mr. Deval is rarely wrong.

07:46.000 --> 07:47.440
He has played for Ranji.

07:47.520 --> 07:49.240
And he was also the Vice-President

07:49.280 --> 07:50.880
of the Bihar Cricket Association.

07:50.920 --> 07:52.320
Understood?
- Yes, sir.

07:59.960 --> 08:01.440
Pause here.

08:05.640 --> 08:07.400
Who commissioned this AV, Roy?

08:07.440 --> 08:09.720
Mr. Sinha did.

08:09.920 --> 08:11.280
There's something I must
tell him over the phone.

08:11.320 --> 08:12.360
Remind me later.

08:12.400 --> 08:13.520
Yes, sir.

08:14.440 --> 08:18.760
Rakesh, we're in the 90s now.
- Right, sir.

08:19.120 --> 08:22.600
Change the sitar music
in the background.

08:22.960 --> 08:23.840
Yes, sir.

08:23.880 --> 08:26.520
And reshoot the ground
footage in three months.

08:27.680 --> 08:31.040
Is there anything wrong
with the ground footage?

08:33.120 --> 08:34.559
You call this a ground!

08:35.240 --> 08:36.679
Is this where you want
our children to practice

08:36.720 --> 08:38.480
and compete with kids
from other states?

08:38.880 --> 08:41.200
Reshoot this ground
in three months.

08:41.919 --> 08:43.480
We're putting in
a turf wicket here.

08:43.919 --> 08:45.760
I'm going to completely
revamp this stadium.

08:45.960 --> 08:49.400
Sir, may I ask you something,
if you don't mind?

08:50.000 --> 08:52.400
Why aren't Bihar's players
regulars in the national team?

08:52.440 --> 08:53.840
Isn't that what you want to ask?

08:53.880 --> 08:54.920
Yes, sir.

08:55.040 --> 08:58.520
We love politics more
than cricket. Get it?

08:59.160 --> 09:00.280
See you.
- Yes.

09:06.040 --> 09:07.680
Budhia.
- Yes, sir.

09:07.720 --> 09:08.960
Why haven't you
watered the ground yet?

09:09.080 --> 09:11.360
The pump operator, Pan Singh,
is refusing.

09:12.520 --> 09:13.480
What do you mean
by he's refusing?

09:13.520 --> 09:15.240
He's saying
that there's no water.

09:17.120 --> 09:18.720
Get him here.
- Yes, sir.

09:21.560 --> 09:25.240
What's going on?
- Don't worry, sir.

09:27.520 --> 09:30.280
Pan Singh, Mr. Deval is
calling you to the ground.

09:34.440 --> 09:36.120
What happened now?

09:38.880 --> 09:40.840
Be strict with these people.
- Yes, sir.

09:40.880 --> 09:42.400
Do you see
the condition of the ground?

09:42.720 --> 09:44.720
Hello, sir.
- Hello.

09:45.200 --> 09:46.360
Why haven't you
watered the ground yet?

09:46.480 --> 09:49.800
Sir, right now the water is being
supplied to the family quarters.

09:50.120 --> 09:51.560
I'll water the ground
if there's any left.

09:51.760 --> 09:53.920
What's the problem
in doing it now?

09:54.240 --> 09:56.000
If the family quarters
don't get enough

09:56.400 --> 09:58.040
I'll have to answer to them.

09:58.800 --> 10:00.200
And what about the stadium?

10:01.640 --> 10:02.920
If the families need to eat

10:02.960 --> 10:05.520
the children also need to play.
- Yes, sir.

10:06.640 --> 10:08.200
Do you expect the
children to play on this?

10:08.360 --> 10:11.120
You're right, sir.

10:11.280 --> 10:12.720
Then water the ground right now.

10:12.760 --> 10:15.120
Sir,
it'll be wrong to do it now.

10:15.800 --> 10:17.040
I have a suggestion.

10:17.280 --> 10:19.440
I'll water the field
at night after 11.

10:19.520 --> 10:20.880
That will solve everyone's problems.

10:21.960 --> 10:23.240
What time do you sleep?

10:24.480 --> 10:25.960
Currently I'm in the morning shift.

10:26.200 --> 10:27.880
So I sleep by 9 p.m.

10:28.960 --> 10:30.440
Can you sleep at 9 p.m.
and wake up at 11 p.m. again?

10:30.520 --> 10:32.160
Yes, don't worry about that.

10:33.960 --> 10:35.720
Goodbye, sir.

10:43.960 --> 10:45.040
What do you mean he won't play?

10:45.240 --> 10:46.120
Try to understand, Mrs. Shukla.

10:46.160 --> 10:47.240
The match is just three days away

10:47.280 --> 10:49.040
and now you're saying he won't play.

10:49.080 --> 10:50.720
If he doesn't play, who's
going to do the wicket-keeping?

10:50.760 --> 10:52.680
His father is getting furious.

10:52.720 --> 10:54.120
His board exams are
just around the corner.

10:54.160 --> 10:56.160
If he wastes his time playing cricket

10:56.200 --> 10:57.560
then when will he study?

10:57.640 --> 10:59.160
But the exams start
after two months.

10:59.240 --> 11:02.320
Exactly my point,
only two months are left.

11:02.360 --> 11:04.560
Wicket-keeping won't
do him any good.

11:05.000 --> 11:07.600
And if his percentage
drops even by a notch

11:07.640 --> 11:09.920
his father will create a ruckus.

11:10.160 --> 11:12.360
Look,
your son plays really well.

11:12.440 --> 11:14.960
You're ruining his life
for a few marks.

11:15.040 --> 11:16.520
Let him play,
he'll make it really big someday.

11:16.560 --> 11:17.560
How big?

11:17.600 --> 11:20.720
At the most he'll go
from Ranchi to Jamshedpur.

11:21.000 --> 11:22.840
No, Mr. Banerjee,
please spare him.

11:22.960 --> 11:25.160
His father wants to
make him a lawyer.

11:25.200 --> 11:26.760
He wants to send him to Kolkata.

11:26.800 --> 11:29.400
Come, Pintu. Come on.
- Mrs. Shukla.

11:30.400 --> 11:32.040
Listen to me!

11:34.160 --> 11:35.480
His present is still uncertain

11:35.600 --> 11:37.160
and she wants to shape his future.

12:07.600 --> 12:08.920
Chittu, come here.

12:08.960 --> 12:10.160
Yes, sir?

12:10.800 --> 12:13.320
Who's that boy?
- Goalkeeper? - Yes.

12:13.680 --> 12:16.080
That's Mahi. He's my classmate.

12:16.160 --> 12:17.800
Look, don't tell him I asked.

12:17.880 --> 12:19.720
Ask him if he's interested
in playing cricket.

12:41.600 --> 12:42.400
What did he say?

12:42.480 --> 12:45.680
He said, 'Are you mad?
Who wants to play with a tiny ball?'

12:52.200 --> 12:53.520
Come..

12:53.840 --> 12:54.960
Come.

13:03.040 --> 13:05.200
Come..

13:07.200 --> 13:09.760
Jayanti,
tell Mahi to do his homework!

13:10.880 --> 13:13.240
Mahi, do your homework!

13:13.920 --> 13:15.400
Just five more minutes.

13:18.360 --> 13:19.800
Come.

13:21.560 --> 13:23.200
Mahi, dad is home!

13:34.240 --> 13:37.440
'...the world of architecture.
Architecture..'

13:37.520 --> 13:40.880
'The Taj Mahal is one of the seven..'
- Here.

13:40.920 --> 13:43.760
'...wonders of the world..'

13:43.800 --> 13:46.960
'Which he built for his wife..'

13:47.040 --> 13:49.040
They sat down to study
after they saw my cycle.

13:49.120 --> 13:50.360
Of course.

13:50.680 --> 13:52.960
Why don't you two fix
a daily routine for yourselves?

13:53.520 --> 13:55.960
2 hours for studies and
then 2 hours for playing.

13:56.280 --> 13:58.080
Mahi has already fixed
a routine for himself.

13:58.120 --> 14:01.040
2 hours for playing and then
another 2 hours for playing.

14:01.960 --> 14:04.480
Let it be, I'll deal with them.

14:06.440 --> 14:08.120
I have to go tonight.

14:09.160 --> 14:11.840
Why? Overtime again?
- No. It's a small thing.

14:13.080 --> 14:15.360
You haven't been
well the past two days.

14:15.920 --> 14:16.920
Let it be.

14:16.960 --> 14:18.080
I've already said that I'll do it.

14:18.280 --> 14:19.960
It's not too much work.

14:20.080 --> 14:21.640
The ground has completely
dried up as well.

14:22.680 --> 14:26.880
'Monuments are built by..
Between 16th and 17th century..'

14:34.360 --> 14:35.840
Come back soon.

15:45.200 --> 15:47.080
Budhia, switch on the lights
and start the water-pump!

15:47.120 --> 15:48.240
Okay!

16:25.720 --> 16:27.000
Good morning.
- Good morning, sir.

16:27.040 --> 16:28.360
Good morning.
- Good morning, sir.

16:28.400 --> 16:29.800
Did you do your
history homework?

16:29.880 --> 16:30.920
Hey!

16:32.440 --> 16:34.480
Sir, me?
- Yes. Come here.

16:36.880 --> 16:38.040
What's your name?

16:38.080 --> 16:39.640
Mahendra Singh Dhoni.

16:40.120 --> 16:41.280
You're a good goalkeeper.

16:41.320 --> 16:43.000
I saw you play yesterday.
Keep it up.

16:43.280 --> 16:44.600
Thank you, sir.

16:45.080 --> 16:46.800
What other sports do you like?

16:47.080 --> 16:48.920
Badminton. Table Tennis.

16:49.400 --> 16:51.520
Would you like to play cricket?
- No, sir.

16:52.840 --> 16:54.240
No interest in cricket?

16:54.440 --> 16:55.600
Not really.

16:57.000 --> 17:00.600
Scared of playing with a hard ball?
- No, sir.

17:00.760 --> 17:03.280
The wicket-keeper trials
are after school today.

17:03.520 --> 17:04.920
Play for me.

17:05.200 --> 17:06.520
Okay, sir.

17:08.800 --> 17:10.319
Excuse me, sir.

17:11.839 --> 17:13.800
I'm not scared of playing
with the hard ball.

17:13.839 --> 17:15.079
Thank you, sir.

17:21.960 --> 17:24.720
Catch the ball!

17:25.560 --> 17:27.720
Yes, catch it.

17:27.760 --> 17:30.240
Catch it.
Yes. Don't drop it.

17:30.280 --> 17:31.160
Oh!

17:31.280 --> 17:32.560
You're completely useless

17:32.640 --> 17:35.320
in sports and studies.

17:36.480 --> 17:38.240
Let's see you catch some more.
Come on.

17:41.880 --> 17:44.520
What's your problem?
Can't you see the ball?

17:44.840 --> 17:46.960
It's a red ball!
Can't you see it?

17:47.000 --> 17:48.840
You can't do anything right.

17:48.880 --> 17:50.520
Good afternoon, sir.
- Good afternoon.

17:50.560 --> 17:51.960
Shabbir, give him a pair of gloves.

17:52.040 --> 17:53.520
Wear those gloves.
You come here.

17:55.440 --> 17:57.560
Now go.
Go, stand on the mark, come on.

18:02.160 --> 18:03.840
Ready?
- Yes, sir.

18:04.040 --> 18:05.120
Throw.

18:07.920 --> 18:09.360
You don't
punch the ball in cricket.

18:09.440 --> 18:12.040
You catch the ball. Understood?
- Yes, sir.

18:12.120 --> 18:13.240
Ready.

18:13.680 --> 18:15.600
Come on, throw, throw.

18:18.200 --> 18:20.680
Are you trying to
catch a ball or a fish?

18:20.840 --> 18:23.400
Catch it. No problem!

18:23.440 --> 18:25.080
Concentrate!

18:25.120 --> 18:29.720
Keep your eyes on the ball
right till the end!

18:29.760 --> 18:32.360
Very good!
Yes, that's it. Correct.

18:32.960 --> 18:34.440
Very good. Very good.

18:35.360 --> 18:36.600
Very good.

18:38.240 --> 18:39.600
That's it! That's it!

18:42.120 --> 18:43.280
Very good!

18:48.880 --> 18:50.560
Good. Very good!

18:50.600 --> 18:52.600
Come here.
Hey, stop!

18:54.440 --> 18:56.160
Would you like to do wicket-keeping
for the school team?

18:56.560 --> 18:58.240
Sir, I like to bat more than
anything in cricket.

18:58.320 --> 19:00.200
Concentrate on your
wicket-keeping first.

19:01.240 --> 19:03.440
But sir..
- I said wicket-keeping.

19:04.440 --> 19:07.880
You must practise everyday
for two hours after school. Okay?

19:10.800 --> 19:12.320
Can I keep the gloves?

19:12.920 --> 19:16.040
Keep them.

19:16.600 --> 19:18.360
Shabbir,
give him the inners as well.

19:19.200 --> 19:20.080
Take care of them.

19:20.160 --> 19:21.440
Yes, sir.
- They are school property.

19:21.480 --> 19:23.280
I'm only allowing this
as a special case.

19:27.960 --> 19:29.240
Sister!

19:29.400 --> 19:30.840
Sister!
- What?

19:30.920 --> 19:33.480
Look.
- What is that?

19:33.560 --> 19:34.840
Wicket-keeping gloves.

19:34.880 --> 19:36.240
I've been selected
for the school team.

19:36.480 --> 19:38.080
All play and no work
will ruin your life.

19:38.120 --> 19:39.840
All work and no play
will help you succeed.

19:40.040 --> 19:42.520
All work and no
play will ruin my life.

19:42.720 --> 19:45.000
All play and no work
will make me succeed.

19:46.080 --> 19:47.160
Mahi, wait!

19:47.240 --> 19:48.360
Mahi!

19:53.920 --> 19:57.280
Mom,
Mahi wants to say something.

19:57.480 --> 19:58.560
Tell her.

19:58.960 --> 20:00.320
What is it, Mahi?

20:00.400 --> 20:04.040
Mom, I've been selected
for the school's cricket team.

20:04.320 --> 20:05.440
So?

20:05.960 --> 20:08.720
So, I have to practise for
2 hours every day after school.

20:08.840 --> 20:09.920
And your studies?

20:09.960 --> 20:11.360
I'll do it when I come back.

20:11.400 --> 20:14.400
Honestly.
Just talk to dad.

20:14.440 --> 20:15.440
Please, Mom.

20:15.480 --> 20:18.160
And his studies?
- He'll do it after he comes back.

20:18.800 --> 20:20.800
What do you mean by he'll do it?
- He'll manage.

20:21.160 --> 20:22.720
His heart is set on it.

20:28.160 --> 20:29.280
Come here.

20:31.120 --> 20:32.400
Yes, Dad.

20:35.000 --> 20:37.120
When did you catch
this cricket fever?

20:37.320 --> 20:38.640
Today.

20:42.440 --> 20:44.600
Fine, but don't let
it affect your studies.

20:44.640 --> 20:46.200
Not even a bit.
- Yes.

20:48.160 --> 20:49.600
What am I?

20:50.760 --> 20:54.480
What do I do?
- You're a pump operator.

20:55.320 --> 20:57.320
That's why I keep insisting
that you study.

20:58.600 --> 21:00.480
Don't be like me.

21:01.840 --> 21:03.280
Sports has its own importance.

21:04.720 --> 21:08.120
But only if you study hard
will you be successful.

21:08.160 --> 21:09.400
Understand?

21:13.600 --> 21:14.800
Yes.

21:16.320 --> 21:17.360
Go.

21:21.280 --> 21:23.800
It's so hard to get
a government job these days.

21:23.880 --> 21:26.960
"Smear 'Malai' on the face
of the sun."

21:27.000 --> 21:30.040
"Ride the foolish clouds."

21:32.480 --> 21:36.240
"Smear 'Malai' on the face
of the sun."

21:36.280 --> 21:39.120
"Ride the foolish clouds."

21:39.160 --> 21:42.440
"We open our books to study"

21:42.520 --> 21:45.520
"and they teach us
about the Panipat War."

21:45.560 --> 21:48.720
"Listen to your heart
and be a brave-heart."

21:48.760 --> 21:51.480
"Fear will get you nothing."

21:51.600 --> 21:54.280
"All work and no play
will help you succeed."

21:54.320 --> 21:57.880
"All play and no work
will ruin your life."

21:57.920 --> 22:00.440
"All work and no play
will ruin your life."

22:00.480 --> 22:04.000
"All play and no work
will make you succeed."

22:18.320 --> 22:19.440
How much is that for?

22:19.760 --> 22:21.040
Rs. 400 for that one.
- Oh, no!

22:21.080 --> 22:22.880
And this one?
- Rs. 200.

22:23.320 --> 22:25.040
Fine, how much for this one?
- Rs. 80.

22:25.120 --> 22:26.800
Hurry up,
I'm getting late for practice.

22:26.840 --> 22:29.000
Who told you to schedule
the practice on Sunday?

22:29.080 --> 22:31.680
Yes
- Fine, final price is 60.

22:31.800 --> 22:33.240
I won't pay more than 50.

22:33.320 --> 22:34.360
He won't give it.
Let's go, let's go.

22:34.440 --> 22:36.320
50 isn't possible.
- Okay, fine.

22:36.360 --> 22:37.720
Ma'am..

22:38.960 --> 22:40.560
Good shot! Who's next?

22:43.440 --> 22:45.360
What are you doing?
You're bowling so short.

22:45.760 --> 22:47.000
Come on, Sanjay.

22:49.520 --> 22:51.880
Good ball, good ball. Next!

22:54.640 --> 22:56.160
Great!
- Good shot again!

22:56.240 --> 22:58.120
Next, quickly!

22:59.520 --> 23:02.080
Aakash?
- Yes, Mahi.

23:02.480 --> 23:04.120
Will you let me bat for a while?

23:04.320 --> 23:06.560
Mr. Banerjee only
makes me do wicket-keeping.

23:06.960 --> 23:08.400
What are you doing?
Bowl properly.

23:08.720 --> 23:10.520
No.. I said 50.

23:10.800 --> 23:12.280
Okay, 55 and it's yours.

23:12.320 --> 23:13.960
Oh, God!
- 50 and that's final.

23:14.000 --> 23:15.040
Just give it to her!
- Okay.

23:15.080 --> 23:17.760
Weigh it first. Come on.
- Quickly.

23:17.880 --> 23:20.080
Give him 50.
- I am, hold on.

23:20.480 --> 23:22.200
Fine?
- Fine, fine.

23:22.240 --> 23:23.560
Cut the pieces.

23:33.720 --> 23:36.200
Mahi is stretching like
he's going to whack the ball.

23:45.960 --> 23:48.040
Sanjay, bowl him an easy ball.

23:54.160 --> 23:55.480
Whoa!

23:55.520 --> 23:57.040
Good shot, Mahi, good shot!

23:57.080 --> 24:00.080
Here's your money.
Take it.

24:00.520 --> 24:01.960
What's the hurry?

24:02.040 --> 24:04.320
You don't understand anything.
- Yes!

24:04.360 --> 24:05.720
Because you're the
only smart one!

24:05.760 --> 24:07.000
Taking me shopping during
practice hours.

