24:44.400 --> 24:47.160
Good shot, Mahi!

25:28.640 --> 25:31.040
Hello, Mr. Pan Singh.
- Hello. Hello.

25:32.240 --> 25:36.440
Let's buy some bangles.
- Yes, sure.

25:45.800 --> 25:47.360
Mom, Mom.

25:47.600 --> 25:48.880
Mom, listen.

25:48.920 --> 25:50.120
Huh?

25:50.320 --> 25:51.720
What?
- Mom..

25:52.120 --> 25:54.080
Mom.
Can I buy that?

25:54.120 --> 25:56.960
Lord Hanuman?
- No, the one next to that.

25:58.200 --> 25:59.960
Which God is that?

26:00.000 --> 26:01.800
And that's a strange
crown he's wearing.

26:01.920 --> 26:03.240
What will you do with that?

26:03.640 --> 26:05.240
Mom,
just buy that for me please.

26:18.720 --> 26:21.760
Look, he has hung Sachin's
poster on the wall.

26:21.880 --> 26:23.480
Why did you buy it?

26:23.600 --> 26:24.840
What could I do?

26:25.600 --> 26:29.360
I saw his expression
and I couldn't say no.

26:31.720 --> 26:33.760
Don't think too much.

26:33.800 --> 26:36.440
