Will that make you happy?

26:48.960 --> 26:50.440
Yes, it will.

26:51.520 --> 26:54.640
What if Mahi isn't happy with that?

26:55.800 --> 26:56.920
What do you mean?

26:58.040 --> 27:01.440
I watch him

27:01.840 --> 27:03.640
and kids his age.

27:04.960 --> 27:07.040
My heart says

27:07.880 --> 27:09.960
