at these small milestones.

27:10.960 --> 27:12.640
Just wait and watch.

27:15.960 --> 27:18.960
From the bus stand end,
right arm over the wicket.

27:19.240 --> 27:22.120
And that's.. That's a miss!
- Oh, no!

27:22.280 --> 27:23.840
That was a really good ball.

27:23.920 --> 27:25.320
Hey..
- Straight to the keeper's hand.

27:25.400 --> 27:28.080
It's getting really hard
for DAV School to score.

27:28.360 --> 27:30.080
Prashant Sharma is
a really good bowler.

27:30.160 --> 27:32.640
In the previous match
he took three wickets

27:32.680 --> 27:33.880
and did a hat-trick.

27:33.920 --> 27:35.560
Making things difficult
for DAV School.

27:35.600 --> 27:38.600
Let's see what DAV School's
strategy is going to be.

27:39.080 --> 27:40.920
Come on. Come on!

27:41.520 --> 27:44.480
The match is
at an interesting point.

27:44.520 --> 27:47.960
DAV needs 12 runs to win,
with just 4 balls remaining

27:48.040 --> 27:49.560
and 3 wickets in hand.

27:49.880 --> 27:51.200
And now the next ball.

27:51.320 --> 27:53.160
And that's out!

27:53.200 --> 27:55.520
He's clean bowled.

27:56.400 --> 27:59.320
It seems like the match is
slipping out of DAV's hands.

27:59.360 --> 28:01.320
DAV needs 12 runs to win.

28:01.360 --> 28:02.960
There are 3 balls left

28:03.040 --> 28:04.760
and I can see a new player
coming to the ground.

28:04.800 --> 28:07.960
Careful.
- His name is Mahendra Singh Dhoni.

28:08.280 --> 28:09.320
I know you won't listen.

28:09.360 --> 28:12.280
Will you score if I give you
the strike? - I'll try.

28:12.360 --> 28:13.960
Then I would rather try myself.

28:17.400 --> 28:19.960
Come on..

28:24.480 --> 28:26.480
It's going to be tough
for DAV School.

28:28.320 --> 28:30.640
Prashant Sharma is bowling
from the Khairali end.

28:30.920 --> 28:32.800
Prashant Sharma, gesturing

28:32.840 --> 28:34.320
for a change in the
fielding positions.

28:36.240 --> 28:39.360
Mahendra Singh Dhoni ready for
bowler Prashant Sharma.

28:39.400 --> 28:41.760
Bowling right hand over the wicket.

28:42.440 --> 28:44.360
