for DAV Shyamali.

28:59.480 --> 29:01.680
Two balls to go
and six runs required.

29:01.720 --> 29:03.200
Prashant Sharma.

29:07.080 --> 29:08.560
Six!

29:08.600 --> 29:10.400
Yay!

29:11.040 --> 29:12.400
Hit towards the bus stand!

29:12.440 --> 29:16.600
With that six, DAV has stolen
the match from under their nose.

29:22.200 --> 29:24.760
The sky is clear and it's
a good a day to play cricket.

29:24.800 --> 29:26.760
DAV Shyamali
and Khairali's captains

29:27.080 --> 29:28.840
are in the middle of
the field for the toss.

29:29.640 --> 29:30.840
Heads.

29:34.000 --> 29:35.440
