- Okay.

29:49.480 --> 29:51.320
Excuse me, sir.
- What?

29:51.520 --> 29:53.480
I haven't got a chance to bat
for the last 8 matches.

29:53.560 --> 29:55.320
You'll get it today,
their bowling is really strong.

29:55.360 --> 29:56.960
With your permission,
can I open today?

29:57.240 --> 29:58.520
What?

29:58.920 --> 30:01.040
Sir, Shabbir and Anuj
open every time.

30:01.080 --> 30:02.560
Give me one chance too.

30:02.600 --> 30:04.080
Fine,
we'll see in the next match.

30:04.360 --> 30:06.920
The next match is with RPS.
- So?

30:07.280 --> 30:09.440
What's the point in
scoring against a weak team?

30:09.960 --> 30:11.720
They are both
padded up and ready.

30:11.760 --> 30:13.120
I'll talk to them, sir.
Just a minute.

30:13.160 --> 30:14.560
Hey, listen!

30:16.400 --> 30:17.360
Mr. Shukla

30:17.440 --> 30:19.960
both teams are really enthusiastic.

30:20.240 --> 30:22.800
Anything can happen in today's game.

30:22.920 --> 30:26.080
That's what I predict.
Let's see what happens.

30:26.120 --> 30:28.240
Sir, Anuj is ready.
Can Shabbir and I open?

30:28.280 --> 30:30.880
First tell me what you said to them.

30:31.440 --> 30:33.720
Mr. Banerjee!
- Yes, coming.

30:37.920 --> 30:39.120
Go.
- Thank you, sir.

30:39.160 --> 30:40.640
Listen.
- Yes, sir?

30:40.680 --> 30:43.360
Don't be in a hurry to return.
- Yes, sir.

30:44.800 --> 30:47.280
Shabbir Hussain and
Mahendra Singh Dhoni

30:47.400 --> 30:50.720
will be opening
for DAV Shyamali.

30:51.640 --> 30:53.000
Play carefully.

30:53.080 --> 30:54.240
Mr. Banerjee won't
give you a second chance.

30:54.320 --> 30:56.560
I'll take the strike,
just don't get me run out.

30:56.600 --> 30:57.600
What?

30:58.200 --> 30:59.760
Mahendra Singh Dhoni

30:59.840 --> 31:01.800
usually comes in at No. 6

31:01.840 --> 31:03.200
but is set to open today.

31:03.280 --> 31:05.800
What are your thoughts on
this Mr. Tiwari? Right or wrong?

31:05.840 --> 31:07.960
Let's see how the match plays out.

31:14.880 --> 31:16.200
First ball of the over.

31:16.440 --> 31:19.960
Shorakat Chowdhary.
Pacing towards the pitch

31:20.320 --> 31:21.960
and the first ball.

31:22.040 --> 31:23.280
And he has smashed it!

31:23.320 --> 31:26.280
Six runs!
- Brilliant!

31:26.320 --> 31:29.280
Wait a minute, I know that boy!

31:29.560 --> 31:31.640
He's a hard hitter, Mr. Shukla.

31:31.880 --> 31:34.160
He hit two straight sixes

31:34.200 --> 31:36.320
and won the last
match for his team.

31:36.360 --> 31:37.560
He's really good!

31:37.720 --> 31:39.840
How many viewers do you
see on the ground right now?

31:39.920 --> 31:41.640
Roughly 15-16 people.
Why are you asking?

31:41.720 --> 31:43.800
Mr. Shukla,
let this boy play for an hour.

31:43.880 --> 31:46.720
And you'll see a different
scenario altogether.

31:51.960 --> 31:54.360
That's superb!
- Beautiful shot!

31:57.360 --> 31:59.760
Six runs!
- Great shot!

32:09.200 --> 32:12.560
Mahi is smashing the ball.
- What do you mean?

32:12.600 --> 32:13.640
How many wickets did we lose?

32:13.720 --> 32:15.040
He has opened the innings today.

32:15.800 --> 32:17.280
Girish, look after the shop.

32:21.280 --> 32:22.680
The next bowler is ready

32:22.880 --> 32:24.560
and he has bowled to Dhoni.

32:24.880 --> 32:27.880
And Dhoni has hit that
hard for 4 runs!

32:27.920 --> 32:30.360
Awesome!
- Well done!

32:38.080 --> 32:39.560
What a player!

32:42.840 --> 32:45.560
Amazing!
And that's a 50!

32:45.600 --> 32:47.920
Amazing!
You're playing really well.

32:47.960 --> 32:49.960
Keep at it. Play carefully.

33:05.800 --> 33:07.640
Ma'am, Mahi is smashing the ball!

33:08.280 --> 33:10.840
That's great!
- That calls for a holiday. - Yes.

33:20.240 --> 33:23.480
Dhoni's batting is
spreading its magic.

33:23.680 --> 33:27.800
Children are
flocking to the ground!

33:30.080 --> 33:31.880
Yes, yes, yes!

33:39.400 --> 33:42.640
That's great!
That's Dhoni's second century!

33:44.840 --> 33:47.280
Double century for him!

33:49.160 --> 33:51.200
I'm proud of you.

34:00.120 --> 34:02.640
He has unravelled the opposition!

34:12.719 --> 34:15.400
Hello. - Hello, please
connect me to Mr. Somi.

34:15.440 --> 34:16.960
Please hold, I'll connect you.

34:22.840 --> 34:23.960
Call for you.

34:26.480 --> 34:28.679
Hello.
- Hello, Mr. Somi.

34:28.760 --> 34:30.040
Param speaking from Ranchi.

34:30.920 --> 34:34.159
Param, I gave you this
number only for emergencies.

34:34.199 --> 34:35.320
This is an emergency.

34:35.360 --> 34:37.080
Remember that boy, Dhoni?

34:37.719 --> 34:40.239
I spoke to you about
sponsoring his cricket kit.

34:40.320 --> 34:43.159
Yes, you keep calling
up regularly for him

34:43.199 --> 34:44.840
and I keep saying no.

34:44.880 --> 34:46.400
What's his name? Dhoni.

34:46.440 --> 34:47.840
Yes, that's him.

34:47.880 --> 34:50.480
You know,
he scored 213 runs in 150 balls.

34:50.520 --> 34:51.520
And in a single day.

34:51.639 --> 34:53.719
His game is getting
better day by day.

34:53.840 --> 34:55.280
I just wanted to
give you this good news.

34:55.520 --> 34:56.679
Okay, are you done?

34:56.760 --> 34:58.240
Can I hang up now?
- Yes.

34:58.320 --> 35:00.480
I'll call you again tomorrow
for the sponsorship.

35:00.520 --> 35:02.240
And I'm coming
to Jalandhar at the month's end.

35:02.280 --> 35:03.880
Goodbye.
- Don't come!

35:04.080 --> 35:05.520
Hello, Param.

35:05.800 --> 35:07.160
Lord.

35:07.240 --> 35:08.520
How much?

35:10.760 --> 35:12.200
'And now for sports news.'

35:12.760 --> 35:17.040
'India was eliminated from
the 1999 World Cup competition.'

35:17.440 --> 35:19.440
'While playing against
New Zealand in Trent Bridge'

35:19.480 --> 35:20.680
'India won the toss'

35:20.720 --> 35:22.640
'and elected to bat first.'

35:23.080 --> 35:25.120
'Ajay Jadeja made
the highest score'

35:25.160 --> 35:26.640
'of 76 runs on behalf of India.'

35:27.200 --> 35:30.280
'India made 251 runs in 50 overs.'

35:30.760 --> 35:32.440
'The New Zealand team..'

35:34.560 --> 35:36.120
Come on, Mahi, it's quite late.

35:36.760 --> 35:40.040
Chotu, I don't think this one's
going to last for too long.

35:40.280 --> 35:42.440
Why do you hit so hard?
Use it gently.

35:42.520 --> 35:45.080
I hit gently.
It's you who thinks I hit hard.

35:45.440 --> 35:47.160
Girish, close the shop.

35:48.880 --> 35:51.600
May I ride it?
- Here.

36:14.520 --> 36:18.680
Chotu,
the MRF bat which Sachin uses..

36:19.040 --> 36:20.160
How much does that cost?

36:20.200 --> 36:21.800
MRF only makes tires.

36:21.960 --> 36:25.240
Sachin has been paid to
put the MRF sticker on his bat.

36:25.520 --> 36:26.840
People pay good players

36:26.880 --> 36:28.920
to put their stickers on their bats.

36:29.120 --> 36:30.320
That's great.

36:30.800 --> 36:33.920
And Dad, everyone says
that Mahi plays really well.

36:33.960 --> 36:34.960
And if he keeps playing like this

36:35.040 --> 36:36.480
someday he will make it really big.

36:39.080 --> 36:41.080
When do his exams begin?
- Day after tomorrow.

36:41.160 --> 36:44.600
And you know, his Under-19
trials are coming up too.

36:44.640 --> 36:45.720
Just a second.

36:57.760 --> 37:00.720
How are your studies coming along?
- Just fine.

37:01.200 --> 37:02.480
My exams start day after tomorrow.

37:04.400 --> 37:05.880
Will you pass?

37:07.200 --> 37:09.320
That's what I want
to talk to you about.

37:09.800 --> 37:12.520
The Office Leagues
begin day after tomorrow.

37:12.920 --> 37:14.600
Trials begin at 11 a.m. everyday.

37:15.720 --> 37:17.240
But will you appear
for your exams?

37:17.720 --> 37:19.280
The exam starts at 8 a.m.

37:19.680 --> 37:21.920
If I finish my paper by 10:30

37:21.960 --> 37:24.800
and catch the 10:45 passenger train

37:25.080 --> 37:26.640
I'll make it to the ground on time.

37:26.840 --> 37:27.920
Yes.

37:28.080 --> 37:31.800
Will you finish your 3 hour
paper in 2.5 hours?

37:33.360 --> 37:36.640
It's difficult,
but I'll get through.

37:38.280 --> 37:39.840
That must be Chittu with the notes.

37:39.880 --> 37:41.200
I'll be right back.

37:43.040 --> 37:43.880
What?

37:43.960 --> 37:47.320
Listen, listen! - Water.
- Don't worry so much.

37:47.360 --> 37:48.800
Drink some water.
- I'll drink the water

37:48.840 --> 37:50.760
but how will he finish his 3 hour
paper in 2.5 hours?

37:50.800 --> 37:52.880
Like I said,
let him do what he's doing.

37:52.920 --> 37:55.480
Leave him be.
You worry too much.

