No, Param.

39:03.280 --> 39:05.920
We never sponsor any
non-established player.

39:06.200 --> 39:07.160
That's not our policy.

39:07.240 --> 39:08.680
Sir, the boy's very special.

39:08.960 --> 39:10.680
He just needs your support.

39:10.760 --> 39:12.880
Exactly, it's not
possible to support him.

39:12.960 --> 39:14.040
Goodbye.

39:18.200 --> 39:19.960
You can support
Pakistani players

39:20.040 --> 39:21.520
but not someone
from our own country.

39:24.320 --> 39:26.840
No drama, no emotional drama..
Understand?

39:28.560 --> 39:30.360
Tell me something.

39:30.440 --> 39:32.120
What's his name?
- Dhoni. - Dhoni.

39:32.200 --> 39:33.800
Is Dhoni like Tendulkar?

39:33.960 --> 39:35.320
No. Dhoni is Dhoni.

39:35.440 --> 39:36.640
All that boy needs
is an opportunity

39:36.720 --> 39:37.880
and someday
he'll make it really big.

39:37.960 --> 39:39.400
And one day you will
remember what I said.

39:39.480 --> 39:40.800
Okay,
when are you going to Ranchi?

39:40.960 --> 39:42.040
My train leaves tonight.

39:42.120 --> 39:43.640
Fine, you go on.
I'll think about it

39:43.720 --> 39:44.720
and get back to you
in two days. Okay?

39:44.800 --> 39:46.120
Then why don't I
stay back for two days?

39:46.400 --> 39:48.320
I'm sure you'll think
of doing some good.

39:48.400 --> 39:49.960
And you'll be doing
that poor boy a favour.

39:50.080 --> 39:51.440
How do you benefit from all this?

39:51.960 --> 39:53.880
Why are you advocating that boy?
What's his name?

39:53.960 --> 39:55.040
Dhoni.
- Yes, Dhoni.

39:55.120 --> 39:56.400
What's your interest in all this?

39:56.560 --> 39:57.880
I have a very big interest.

39:57.960 --> 39:59.240
Even I loved cricket.

39:59.400 --> 40:00.480
But had no talent.

40:00.520 --> 40:01.960
But this boy is really talented.

40:02.080 --> 40:03.600
If he makes it big someday

40:04.040 --> 40:06.560
it will make me feel like
I played too.

40:08.560 --> 40:13.080
