before you"

40:14.120 --> 40:18.960
"as long as you feel this way."

40:19.720 --> 40:24.720
"Your wealth and your treasure"

40:25.520 --> 40:31.080
"are this determination
and this passion of yours."

40:32.280 --> 40:37.440
