whenever I breathe."

02:05:25.160 --> 02:05:31.360
"The crossway of your heart"

02:05:31.400 --> 02:05:37.560
"I pass through every day."

02:05:37.880 --> 02:05:42.160
"You tease me like the free wind"

02:05:42.240 --> 02:05:46.280
